{"tid":2134895,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「以正視聽」中共政府透過核酸檢測，收集香港人DNA，準備建立DNA資料庫，方便日後大規模監控同建立集中營！","createTime":"2020-08-01T05:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T13:45:33.000Z","uid":222970,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c74c7d52b65e9fa7e26fb920fe710e55983e1a26","tid":2134895,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T05:09:45.000Z","msg":"呢件事真係會決定香港人日後嘅生死 <br />\n<br />\n連鐘南山都叫香港人全民檢測 黨員認證就知係伏！<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家配合全民不合作運動，拒絕交出DNA<br />\n<br />\n下面有好多關於DNA嘅新聞，麻煩大家睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>光憑DNA就能繪出你的長相！中國強制「全民體檢」加強監控<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20191205intchinadnaprofiling/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20191205intchinadnaprofiling%2F&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOVwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=569e1889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20191205intchinadnaprofiling/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imUpvao.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimUpvao.jpg&h=dd94d351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國科學家研究以DNA繪製出人臉圖像，圖為2013年一項3D圖像研究。（網路截圖，New York Times/BMC BIOINFORMATICS）<br />\n<br />\n而根據美國《紐約時報》的報導，中國正利用收集自新疆維吾爾族人血液的基因樣本來建構人臉圖像。 目的是打造強化種族歸納（racial profiling）和國家歧視（state discrimination）的工具。<br />\n<br />\n根據《紐約時報》的報導，在新疆的圖木舒克，<span class=\"gold\">中共正進行DNA收集工作，並試圖用DNA的樣本來建造人臉圖像</span>。<br />\n<br />\n光是靠DNA樣本就能描繪出一個人的面部特徵，這聽來像是科幻小說的情節。不過據紐時的報導，這項還在初期開發階段的技術，已可以做出粗略圖像，達成縮小搜索範圍和排除特定嫌疑人的目的。透過DNA表型分析（DNA phenotyping）的技術，科學家可以分析膚色、眼球顏色和祖源等特徵。未來北京當局甚至也可能把DNA樣本所生成的圖像輸入目前正在建設的大規模監控與面部辨識系統，達成加強社會控制的目的。<br />\n<br />\n紐時的報導指出，<span class=\"gold\">DNA表型分析可能引發倫理問題。例如警察可能用來拘捕大量貌似嫌犯的人，或針對某個特定的族裔。更根本的問題是，我們一般人是否有權利拒絕個人的樣本被加進數據庫。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據中國媒體報導，中國目前擁有全世界最大的DNA數據庫，到今年7月為止已經有<span class=\"gold\">超過8000萬份基因檔案</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>警涉濫權取被捕人DNA超出調查所需 疑為建DNA資料庫鋪路</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200704/QU2CCJX54PIDSNCST4CZ2PUJUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FQU2CCJX54PIDSNCST4CZ2PUJUM%2F&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOVwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=1a411f61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200704%2FQU2CCJX54PIDSNCST4CZ2PUJUM%2F&h=922ff092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200704/QU2CCJX54PIDSNCST4CZ2PUJUM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>紐約時報：新疆用DNA繪製人臉加強監控</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=372198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D372198&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOVwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=64e11d43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D372198&h=a900ed37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=372198</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>英媒：中國以體檢名義採集新疆人DNA樣本</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/press-review-42340636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fpress-review-42340636&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOVwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=b7ed5